songs.title: The Ocean
songs.lyrics:
[Verse 1]
Bound up the stairs
I'm in the shower
Do you know I am going to leave you?
Fresh from the shore
Blonde hair is wide
The ocean makes me cry

[Chorus]
I'm in love with a dying man
I'm in love with a dying man
I'm in love, lying in the sand
I'm in love with a dying man
I'm in love with a dying man
I have done everything I can

[Verse 2]
Tell me about Ray and his girl
Did I know Ray is going to meet you?
Love you, I do
Stay here, I won't
The stars fade from your eyes

[Chorus]
I'm in love with a dying man
I'm in love with a dying man
I'm in love, lying in the sand
I'm in love with a dying man
I'm in love with a dying man
I have done everything I can

[Bridge]
One, two, make it fun
Don't trust anyone
One, two, make it fun
Don't trust anyone

[Outro]
I'm in love with a dying man
I'm in love with a dying man
I have done everything I can
